headline: DaVita (DVA) Confirms Ransomware Attack Impacted 2.7M People
summary: DaVita Inc. (NYSE:DVA) is one of the best long-term stocks to invest in according to Warren Buffett. On August 21, the company confirmed that a ransomware attack led to a data breach impacting millions of individuals. The company filed a report with the US Department of Health and Human Services (HHS) Office for Civil Rights […]
